Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi chiamo Conan Edogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.63,0:00:05.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Sono il liceale Shinichi, \Nrimpicciolito da una pillola.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:08.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Anche se sono piccolo, la mia mente\N è quella di un detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:11.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Oggi vedremo la prima parte \Ndi un caso su una crociera.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:13.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Riuscirete lo stesso a capire chi è l'assassino?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:15.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,La verità è sempre una sola!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.00,0:01:52.09,Titolo episodio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\blur1\bord0.1\c&HDEDCC8&\pos(263,122)}Il {*\c&HDDDBC7&}c{*\c&HDCDBC7&}as{*\c&HDCDAC6&}o {*\c&HDBDAC6&}d{*\c&HDBDAC5&}e{*\c&HDAD9C5&}ll{*\c&HD9D9C5&}e {*\c&HD9D8C4&}u{*\c&HD8D8C4&}c{*\c&HD8D8C3&}c{*\c&HD7D7C3&}is{*\c&HD7D7C2&}i{*\c&HD6D7C2&}o{*\c&HD6D6C2&}n{*\c&HD5D6C2&}i \N{*\c&HD4D5C1&}s{*\c&HD4D5C0&}ul{*\c&HD3D4C0&}la {*\c&HD2D4BF&}c{*\c&HD2D3BF&}r{*\c&HD1D3BE&}oc{*\c&HD0D2BE&}ie{*\c&HD0D2BD&}r{*\c&HCFD2BD&}a {*\c&HCFD1BC&}d{*\c&HCED1BC&}i {*\c&HCDD0BC&}l{*\c&HCDD0BB&}us{*\c&HCCCFBB&}s{*\c&HCCCFBA&}o {*\c&HCBCFBA&\fs18}({*\c&HCBCEB9&}p{*\c&HCACEB9&}ri{*\c&HC9CDB9&}m{*\c&HC9CDB8&}a {*\c&HC8CDB8&}p{*\c&HC8CCB7&}ar{*\c&HC7CCB7&}te{*\c&HC6CBB6&}){\c&HC6CBB6&}
